    .desc = A magazine of A19 HV high impact rounds for use in the M4RA custom battle rifle. The M4RA custom battle rifle is the only gun that can chamber these rounds.

ent-RMCMagazineRifleM4SPRA19Incendiary = A19 HV incendiary magazine (10x24mm)
    .desc = A magazine of A19 HV incendiary rounds for use in the M4RA custom battle rifle. The M4RA custom battle rifle is the only gun that can chamber these rounds.

ent-WeaponRifleM4SPRCustom = M4RA custom battle rifle
    .desc = An improvement over the already great M4RA. Able to take A19 rounds, as well as having better control and accuracy at the cost of being harder to use. Can take traditional M4RA mags, at lower damage.
